Titolo: The Cyber Shinobi

Anno: 1990

Descrizione: The Cyber Shinobi (also known as Shinobi Part 2) is a side-scrolling action game produced by Sega that was released for the Master System in 1990. It was the third Shinobi game for the console (if one includes Alex Kidd in Shinobi World) and served as a futuristic-themed sequel to the original Shinobi. The game was released in Canada, Europe, Australia and Brazil, at a time when the Master System was discontinued in other markets.